# Data Fetching, Mutations & Validation

## Data Retrieval — Server Components Only

All data fetching **must** be done inside Server Components. Never fetch data inside Client Components directly.

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD — fetch in a Server Component
export default async function DecksPage() {
  const decks = await getUserDecks();
  return <DeckList decks={decks} />;
}

// ❌ BAD — fetching inside a Client Component
'use client';
export default function DecksPage() {
  const [decks, setDecks] = useState([]);
  useEffect(() => { fetch('/api/decks').then(...) }, []);
}
```

## Mutations — Server Actions Only

Any **insert**, **update**, or **delete** database operation **must** be performed inside a [Server Action](mdc:src/actions), never in API routes or client-side code.

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD — mutation via Server Action
'use server';
export async function createDeck(data: CreateDeckInput) { ... }

// ❌ BAD — mutation in an API route handler or client code
export async function POST(req: Request) {
  const body = await req.json();
  await db.insert(decksTable).values(body);
}
```

## Validation — Zod Required

All data validation **must** use [Zod](https://zod.dev/). Define a Zod schema and derive the TypeScript type from it with `z.infer`.

```typescript
import { z } from 'zod';

const createDeckSchema = z.object({
  name: z.string().min(1).max(100),
  description: z.string().optional(),
});

type CreateDeckInput = z.infer<typeof createDeckSchema>;
```

## Server Action Inputs — Typed & Validated

- **Always** define a TypeScript type for every Server Action parameter (derived from a Zod schema via `z.infer`)
- **Always** validate the input with `.parse()` or `.safeParse()` at the top of the action
- **Never** use `FormData` as the parameter type

```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
'use server';
import { z } from 'zod';

const createDeckSchema = z.object({
  name: z.string().min(1),
});

type CreateDeckInput = z.infer<typeof createDeckSchema>;

export async function createDeck(data: CreateDeckInput) {
  const validated = createDeckSchema.parse(data);
  // proceed with validated data...
}

// ❌ BAD — untyped FormData, no validation
export async function createDeck(formData: FormData) {
  const name = formData.get('name');
  await db.insert(decksTable).values({ name });
}
```
